data.description:
A TRUE GEM with an unbeatable location!  This fabulous ranch home has an amazing open floor plan with a great flow. As soon as you walk in, you are greeted by a contemporary archway and LOTS of natural light. This home has everything you are looking for...fresh interior paint, tile throughout the entire home,updated laundry room with tons of storage, 2 car garage, updated master bathroom with tiled standing shower & walk in closet, updated patio flooring.... perfect for entertaining. Grill and entertain in the completely fenced in backyard....

Location, location, location….easy access to I-85 & I-485. Just two minutes from Earth Fare, Kohl’s, Lowe’s, TJMaxx, Trader Joe’s, so many restaurants and more
